accessibility.text: Alternatively I       find it stronger, more persuasive to have the product be the container at first. Just its shape as it fills up with crystalline water creating intriguing waves. Possibly the Lakmé logo remains silhouetted while     it fills up with water. Then the label appears in      full and it becomes the pack.
